reviews.review_text: The food at this mcdonalds was actually cooked well and was fresh not sitting for an hour

We stopped here for breakfast on a day trip. Its right by the freeway and easy to access. It was very clean and bright which was nice. Their servers were all friendly and helpful. Their breakfast was fresh, hot and made to order. Best McDonalds breakfast Ive had in a long time. I would definitely recommend this location. Kid-friendliness: It was very kid friendly with highchairs and very cleanly.
Excellent service! We were  there on Friday 17 (9 pm) The place is clean, and friendly staff! The manager was responding ,thank you!!!
Amazing staff and well cooked and prepped meals
A warm and fast breakfast for $7 for two people in a cloudy day. I recommend that if you are in rush on in a recess time.
Very nice staff. Always helpful and very kind. The food is the same as every McDonald s   which is I guess what we re all looking for haha. The manager is a great guy too!

I take my everyday morning coffee here and it feels great when you see friendly staff with smile on faces while walking into restaurant. It makes your day starts better! One of staff is Fatima, she is super smart, she see me behind the windows walking in and already places my order if no one is in line and in most cases my coffees ready to pick up at no time. Thanks everyone!
Theyll bring the food to your seat if you have a bunch of kids you cant leave alone  at the table. Its a smaller McDonalds and doesnt have drive-thru.
Its a quick meal on the run. Its a pretty busy spot. Lots of people coming and going. Wheelchair accessibility: Theres wheel chair access into Macdonalds. There are kid chairs and a washroom.

Came in here after one of those Saturday nights with my girlfriend and we were hooked up! FAT! For the time we went in, no one would expect a quality meal we got. To the staff member that gave us fat amounts of fudge, on my hot fudge Sunday, Thank you! To the back cook who made my Mighty Angus meal, Thank you! And to the staff that salted my fries just right, Thank you! Overall, Great staff and Great food. #youblewmeawayMchunks Worth the stop!

Friendly. Efficient. Prompt. Cashier repeats order back and server promptly hands over with a smile the order ready to go including added napkins and ketchup without asking. Covid-19 safety protocols are in place with staff wearing masks, plexiglass, circles on floor where customers stand, and signs on the door for safety numbers and customers to wear masks.

The Kale & Feta cheese breakfast wrap is really good. Went for the meal package. The hash brown was very hot & crispy, but on the oily side. Solution: placed hash brown on a napkin, or two, to draw out excess oil. Service was friendly & prompt at 6:30am.
I love the food and service! And the washrooms have very good hand dryers since theyre nice and quiet! good choice

I visited McDonalds on Lonsdale and 19th and as always, being a scooter I get great service, even from the clients.  Everyone wants to help.  All the staff are great, always smiling and going the extra mile for me.
Great customer service...warm welcoming..kind staff...highly recommended
I bought it from McDonalds and it was good
Very good management. Solved my problem very quickly and kindly. Good food also.
I always order from this location and they are always fast. Clean interior and professional staff.
Always great for a quick bite...friendly staff....
The staff on Lonsdale are really kind. No mistakes and fresh coffee.

I just love coming here.  It makes me feel at home with people and Great Staff. As you know McDonalds food quality such Meals as Burgers, Fries, Sundaes, Garden Salads, and more to the Menu are at High Standards. If thats not all but the Great Tasting Coffee, McCafe Latte,  McCafe Cappuccino,  McCafe Americano, McCafe Expresso, McCafe Iced Mocha, McCafe Deluxe Hot Chocolate, and McCafe Tea.  The List Goes On. I Hope wherever you Go in the World where there is a McDonalds you will experience the same feelings any Ages!!!
McD, you got it goin on. This place is open whenever I go there. Plus they take (Master card.) Their meal deal includes fries. I love this long downhill slide McDs is on, super delishious
Morning staff and manager is awesome. They always make my mornings easier !
Staff was polite and the food came quickly :)
Fast and friendly staff only been here the one time and satisfied.
Most amazing and well designed McDonalds Always busy, but quick and fast service
Service was fast and food was hot and fresh. Restaurant was clean and tidy.
Hi I really like this resturant .they have huge back parking lot and clean resturant with nice costemer service.
Really crowded,not enough space between tables.
I like McDonalds coffee. Stopped here for coffee. It was raining hard and I had a good warm place for my favourite coffee.
The usual McDonalds food, they were quite busy so everything came up hot and fresh.
Coffee is good and dont need to wait long to get it.
Its Mac Donalds store get your food and get out
Excellent when you have the McDonalds app to download their specials.
I am a fan of fries   and here we got 2X fries . BTW, that are new offers on some combos
Local McDonalds in the Lonsdale area, good location and a staff named Iman was very helpful.
Good for quick brakefast alway right place.
Very well prepared good value with coupons
Restaurants nice and clean food is good service was great
Convenient location, open 24 hours and great, cheap food!
McDs, my go to place for fast fun food & fabulous coffee.
Always fast service at this location
Great coffee but too busy place
Place is nice and customer service was awesome..
It s the best place to go if you want to get fat!!!!
I love the food!!! Always fresh
